{"tid":950331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中文大學醫學院：近半北上港男與女性性工作者有性行為","createTime":"2018-12-21T12:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T05:01:54.000Z","uid":144372,"like":225,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"579a20c0adfd3f086a78a650d1b36029b72614fc","tid":950331,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2014/02/10/IN1402100034.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2014%2F02%2F10%2FIN1402100034.htm&d=wDVAXzvVilOAhyVKrYBI7y7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=44e6d52c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2014/02/10/IN1402100034.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n海外已經有研究分析這種入境尋春者的風險。香港中文大學醫學院的調查表明，有近半北上港男與女性性工作者有性行為，而且不是每次都使用安全套的機會百分比高達56%(2004年)。另有研究也表明，有53%曾在與妓女交易前喝酒，而有22%曾在與妓女交易前服用精神科藥物。"},{"pid":"a7b9fb83d435fbadcb2fbe4858dec49c1ecf811c","tid":950331,"uid":126283,"like":140,"dislike":3,"score":137,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"支那式陰道<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5c0c92374b6f499bad1bbbed80054ef9564022","tid":950331,"uid":46042,"like":212,"dislike":8,"score":204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"依家啲男人返大陸 係倍條女 出錢出力做狗 食啲垃圾 <br />\n<br />\n波皮都冇得掂"},{"pid":"668cc54fdc092d243603c7be6e6327348ccb301e","tid":950331,"uid":187108,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d889ff4ce5733a5b5ae65c597de57651f2ff92f1","tid":950331,"uid":43042,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"關sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe86fd90a034e8373d1044dc4a31b6dfd88cfa0","tid":950331,"uid":107364,"like":17,"dislike":53,"score":-36,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}